{"tid":1787504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"除夕煙花匯演取消 應該搞光復香港迎新年","createTime":"2019-12-18T03:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T08:38:19.000Z","uid":128430,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b02aa0810ad9a5a8f83f66dd5cff4912b6577e4","tid":1787504,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"反修例運動下，本港將自2012年後首度取消除夕維港煙花倒數，旅發局表示，今年除夕將改為網上倒數，亦會在維港推出「加強版」幻彩詠香江煙火倒數，活動不會有官員主持，但旅發局會推出有逾萬份獎品的大抽獎供港人參與。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局自2012年除夕起辦煙花倒數，今年將首度取消，改為加強版幻彩詠香江，活動包括在大廈頂樓放煙火，會展則會維持設倒數鐘，倒數節目由Viu TV製作。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以考慮下大家一齊去倒數</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不斷叫口號，由8開始叫光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n各位手足考慮下，電視直播，全世界睇倒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9778427dc14a8cd8b9a9d0d79cedc4eb025c6add","tid":1787504,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7f79ad6d30e4a9c115ca16a946282d3ce23d4197","tid":1787504,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:25:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e361b76ff4b8f97b86b959fbb0556de7639ac7a7","tid":1787504,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641bb004d58e223688822348df72602af6932734","tid":1787504,"uid":317156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"行街都唔得？"},{"pid":"1238d2bd15e275623548e8bc4de88ae4bb8eab7b","tid":1787504,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"竟然係viu唔係CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7405799b3de0797787eff3dcb1ccd9c8d019209f","tid":1787504